ed="T" n="0780a01"/><persName key="A009489">釋良价</persName>，俗姓<name>俞</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000013376"><placeName>會稽</placeName><placeName>諸暨</placeName></placeName>人也。少孺從師<lb
ed="T" n="0780a02"/>于<placeName key="PL000000013364">五洩山寺</placeName>。<date key="j20231162023480" from-iso="+0827-01-01" to-iso="+0827-12-31">年至二十一</date>，方往<placeName key="PL000000023253">嵩山</placeName>具戒<lb
ed="T" n="0780a03"/>焉。登即遊方，見<persName key="A003889">南泉<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，深領玄契。續造<lb
ed="T" n="0780a04"/><persName key="A010501">雲巖</persName>，疑滯頓寢。<date notBefore-iso="+0856-07-19" key="j20339082035056" notAfter-iso="+0859-09-10"><name>大中</name>末</date>，於<placeName key="PL000000057064"><anchor xml:id="beg0780sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>斯</sic><corr>新</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0780sgsz1"/>豐山</placeName><ptr target="#n1614"/>大行禪<lb
ed="T" n="0780a05"/>法。後盛化<placeName key="PL000000019687"><placeName>豫章</placeName><placeName>高安</placeName><placeName>洞山</placeName></placeName>，今<placeName key="PL000000019790">筠州</placeName>也。<persName key="A009489">价</persName>以<lb
ed="T" n="0780a06"/><date key="j20385662038566" when-iso="+0869-04-20"><name>咸通</name>十年<anchor xml:id="beg0780sgsz2"/>己<anchor xml:id="end0780sgsz2"/>丑三月朔旦</date>，命剃髮披衣，令鳴<lb
ed="T" n="0780a07"/>鐘，奄然而往。時弟子輩悲號，<persName key="A009489">价</persName>忽開目而起<lb
ed="T" n="0780a08"/>曰：「夫出家之人心不依物，是真修行。勞生<lb
ed="T" n="0780a09"/>息死<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1590"/>，於悲何有？淪喪於情，太麁著乎？」召主<lb
ed="T" n="0780a10"/>事僧令營齋：「齋畢，<ref type="person" target="#A009489">吾</ref>其逝矣！」然眾心戀慕，<lb
ed="T" n="0780a11"/>從延其日。至<anchor xml:id="beg0780001"/>於<anchor xml:id="end0780001"/><date key="j20385722038572" when-iso="+0869-04-26">七辰</date><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1589"/>，食具方備，<persName key="A009489">价</persName>亦隨齋，<lb
ed="T" n="0780a12"/>謂眾曰：「此齋名愚癡也。」蓋責其無般若<ptr type="glossary" target="#g26"/><lb
ed="T" n="0780a13"/>歟。及僧唱隨意<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1776"/>，曰：「僧家勿事太率，臨行之<lb
ed="T" n="0780a14"/>際，喧動如斯。」至<date key="j20385732038573" when-iso="+0869-04-27">八日</date>浴訖，端坐而絕，春秋<lb
ed="T" n="0780a15"/>六十三，法臘四十二<ptr target="#n1615"/>。勅謚禪師曰<persName key="A009489">悟本</persName>，塔<lb
ed="T" n="0780a16"/>號<placeName key="PL000000056282">慧覺</placeName>矣。</p>
    <p><lb
ed="T" n="0780a17"/>系曰：其却留累日，古亦有之。如<persName key="A009489">价</persName>之來去<lb
ed="T" n="0780a18"/>自由者，近世一人而已。</p>
